Yoh! But The Real Housewives of Johannesburg star Evodia Mogase does not hold back on her words or her luxurious lifestyle. The businesswoman known on the show as the 'madame' has often left viewers gasping as she tries to put the other wives straight. Occasionally tempers boiled over, like that time she clashed with Brinnette and even took to the 'gram to call her out for allegedly borrowing clothes from other people. But her Instagram page is a movie on its own, with a look into Evodia's glamorous life. Cava five moments that killed the 'gram and left many green with envy